br.com.gamemods.regionmanipulator

Class Chunk

  • br.com.gamemods.regionmanipulator.Chunk

  • public class Chunk

    A chunk is piece of 16 x 256 x 16 blocks which is contained in a region file.

    For more information about chunks please check the https://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Chunk.

    The chunk represented here will be raw and unparsed, you will have access to it's NBT data to do any modification as you wish.

    See Also:
    https://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Chunk
